{"tid":1633653,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"滙控傳全球裁員最多1萬人","createTime":"2019-10-07T04:47:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-08T11:42:54.000Z","uid":89046,"like":19,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"19fbc50750a862f77af8f0458456924a6c19dcf6","tid":1633653,"uid":89046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T04:47:05.000Z","msg":"滙控傳全球裁員最多1萬人<br />\n國際財經 | 今日 05:42 經濟日報<br />\n<br />\n《金融時報》引述消息人士稱，滙豐控股(00005)計劃全球裁減最多一萬份職位。<br />\n<br />\n根據報道，這是滙控臨時行政總裁祈耀年(Noel Quinn)上任不久後即決定的全面節流計劃一部分，也是該銀行過去兩年最激進的裁員行動。<br />\n<br />\n滙控未有回應查詢。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9182336e326ed46c174d9588c21099b7862aab75","tid":1633653,"uid":167011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T04:48:08.000Z","msg":"勿拆黨鐵！！全民被罷工！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1633581\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1633581</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n三樣香港人應同樣憎恨既野：<br />\n政府、黑警、黨鐵<br />\n<br />\n呢三樣先係主線<br />\n你個啲乜鳩紅藍店，我理撚得你幾時搞？<br />\n個啲要休息，冇問題，但黨鐵而家咁撚樣你都唔食住上，令到全港自動罷工，咁我真係代表我全力支持既香港政府多謝你為香港既經濟服務<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"382bf0851c08b63759c2af53972b04a8c0175a8e","tid":1633653,"uid":235374,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:06:10.000Z","msg":"大家㩒爆HSBC <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ace1b618efa010030cdf3071f917876c23b17850","tid":1633653,"uid":175194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:08:03.000Z","msg":"好"},{"pid":"e9022d29ee4a2fb5e2cdf8925ba130d1164390e8","tid":1633653,"uid":187201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:11:14.000Z","msg":"又炒"},{"pid":"87db9ca34df812f3fd1ebb509bc72c413dd36653","tid":1633653,"uid":44569,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:12:50.000Z","msg":"香港 IT 部<im